title: HOUR 1- Woody Paige Sep 25, 2020

description:
Woody Paige says he thinks the Nuggets have earned the respect of the Lakers as well as the rest of the nation. Woody tells Dan that Denver could be a destination sports town and team. Woody says that it is crap that Lakers head coach went to the league to complain about the lack of foul calls for Lebron.
